txt.en: 'Are you ready to proceed? Finishing this quest will award completion of Volume III Book 14 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 14 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.

'Are you ready to complete Volume III, Book 14? You will bypass something that will make Made of Lions cry that you didn't care enough to experience for the, we're going to guess here, sixth time.'\n\n'It is your decision. If you would like to skip Volume III Book 14 of the Epic quest, speak to me once more. Meow!'
